text: Manilkara nicholsonii is a species of plant in the family Sapotaceae. It is endemic to South Africa (Natal), and is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== Category:Endangered plants Category:Fruits originating in Africa Category:Flora of South Africa nicholsonii Category:Plants described in 1982 Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
